## Limitations

This report is based on available data and literature up to October 2023. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, including potential biases in media reports and the evolving nature of political dynamics. Additionally, the complexity of political polarization means that not all contributing factors may be fully captured in this report. Further research and updated data may provide additional insights into the causes and effects of political division in America.